window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Seven months ago, Mars Felicity Station stopped communicating. The crew of the </b><b><i>Perihelion </i></b><b>will soon find out why. </b></p> <p>Something went wrong in the Mars Felicity Station. A gate to another reality was opened, and a mysterious alien plague threatens humanity.&nbsp;</p> <p>When communications with the station are cut, the <i>Perihelion </i>crew is sent to find out what happened. Outmatched and unprepared, theyâ€™re forced to make war on this new enemy and rescue what remains of the survivors.&nbsp;</p> <p>Fans of <i>Doom</i> and <i>Aliens</i> will love this international best-selling sci-fi survival series.</p>"; 
